{"tid":740164,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「習像」被吐痰 北京下令2日內撤宣傳物","createTime":"2018-07-12T15:53:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-13T06:58:45.000Z","uid":39464,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"df97fee2c639bb4d81279dc567fe68c415be5d9c","tid":740164,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T15:53:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180712/large/1531397432_de2e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180712%2Flarge%2F1531397432_de2e.jpg&h=962856d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上海一名董姓女子本月初在上海海航大廈前面進行直播，向國家主席習近平的宣傳畫像潑墨，並稱對習恨之入骨，並高呼「反對習近平專制獨裁」。此事似乎帶起了內地毀習像的風潮，twitter流傳多張習近平宣傳畫像被破壞的照片。此外，有消息人士向《蘋果》展示一份通告，內容是關於要求撤走「習像」的宣傳物品，證實了早前的有關謠言。<br />\n<br />\n東莞亦一張精神文明建設委員會通告顯示，上級要求「所有戶外廣告不得使用黨及國家領導人的頭像」。<br />\n這份「特別通告」發於今天（12日），上面寫着「要求大廈各單位立即撤下一切有關習近平同志照片、圖像的海報及宣傳品」，通告並要求各單位於48小時內匯報撤習像進展。<br />\n此外，網上流傳照片可見，習像被吐痰、貼上「假專制，求民主」紙張、被雙頭筆畫花，另有照片可見，中國共產黨的標誌被畫上德國極權納粹標誌。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180712/58434896\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180712%2F58434896&d=aWL1b99BwFmFs2mBFk4FljPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=2d794da4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180712%2F58434896&h=cc57c8b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180712/58434896</a>"},{"pid":"255d9cf38aefd80891a657335734e4af947c2ae1","tid":740164,"uid":14144,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T15:54:56.000Z","msg":"似篤精多過痰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfd24c9e1e8c5fe66eb7ef39730eba7d3f22737f","tid":740164,"uid":36178,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T15:55:58.000Z","msg":"吸精瓶<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53f09baa1ab93b1f4d606d14f4ab4b5cf2f08997","tid":740164,"uid":54337,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T16:38:17.000Z","msg":"連登仔：反了反了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n环球时报：又赢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faadbfb9a588909392f5bbe6540ff758b189614f","tid":740164,"uid":58552,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T16:41:54.000Z","msg":"精黎"},{"pid":"8fa43de0a664b0ccc53f6f2abb65c7db6335f65e","tid":740164,"uid":185184,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T16:44:45.000Z","msg":"張紙唔係寫反專制咩<br />\n點解會變左做假專制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aef7137f22f22566a24901364a50a672235715d3","tid":740164,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T17:43:59.000Z","msg":"掉返係香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7aa2bb79a978cd1b26fc2c94885a000a7f0e786","tid":740164,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T22:47:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90b4c146c3d5ee7b86cbb67f1ab0b612d94bea6d","tid":740164,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T00:14:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/goal.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daec671984c0c342062e3446b742221f81849f4f","tid":740164,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T06:58:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"